data.description: MASSIVE Elegance!  This 3310 square foot FULLY REMODELED home is absolutely immaculate!  Every inch has been skillfully remodeled with careful detail, modern finishes, and artful decor and charm.  5 large bedrooms w/a gorgeous main level primary en-suite with a 5-piece bathroom that looks like it jumped out of a spa magazine!   3 full bathrooms, each one meticulously designed.   2 massive living spaces for entertaining lots of impressed guests!  Giant Chef’s kitchen w/gas range in the center island so you can prepare meals while wowing your guests like Benihana!  Two impressive dining spaces for large dinner parties.  North-facing backyard and back patio and a playground for all the littles. Or relax on the front deck recently re-stained. Lots of RV parking space for all your toys!  1 share of irrigation water! Detached 2-car garage. Easy in-city location close to everything!  NO HOA!  A picket fence dresses the perimeter of the property, as if out of a story book.   Come home to WOW FACTOR and convenience!  Buyer to verify all info and measurements.
